The shuttle will drop you at the airport train station if you are going to Seattle, but on your way back you must walk from the station to the shuttle bus pick up area at the airport(about a 5 to 10 minute walk).	The shuttle runs 24 hours per day, and it makes about three trips per hour (no phone call or reservation is needed).	We took the shuttle from the airport, and then back again to pick up our rental car (save the parking fee).